    "Differential_Diagnosis": {
      "text": "Lymphoma\nMore commonly single lesion in the periventricular white matter or corpus callosum\nCerebral TB\nCharacteristic inflammatory appearance with isodense exudate filling basal cisterns\nFungal infection",
